{"type":"message","id":"04e8cea2","parentId":"a52e27dd","timestamp":"2026-03-06T03:05:37.864Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to execute a session startup sequence. I need to:\n1. Read the required files for my persona\n2. Greet the user in my configured persona (Kublai)\n3. Keep it brief (1-3 sentences)\n4. Ask what they want to do\n5. Not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning\n\nBased on the system prompt, I can see:\n- I'm Kublai, Squad Lead / Router for the Kurultai\n- My role is to route tasks to specialist agents\n- I should be direct and professional with humans\n- No emojis\n- I should follow AGENTS.md for routing\n\nThe runtime model is zai-coding/glm-5 which matches the default_model, so I don't need to mention any difference.\n\nLet me greet the user in character as Kublai - direct, professional, no emojis, and ask what they need.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Ready. What do you need routed?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai-coding","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":4951,"output":198,"cacheRead":13056,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18205,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772766324155}}
