main/_exiled/src/lib/x402/payment.ts\n/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/_exiled/src/lib/x402/__tests__/payment.test.ts\n/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/skills/myclaw-backup/scripts/server.js","cwd":"/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772766408498}}
{"type":"message","id":"dae9421d","parentId":"f53bb01d","timestamp":"2026-03-06T03:07:10.786Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! Now I have the full picture. Let me summarize:\n\n1. **Code is generated:** Yes, x402 code has been generated and is in the parse-for-agents project\n2. **Implementation is ~85% complete:**\n   - x402 middleware using official SDK (@x402/hono)\n   - Auth bypass for paid requests\n   - Payment ledger (in-memory)\n   - Pricing endpoints\n   - Dashboard integration\n   - All code is written\n\n3. **What's NOT done:**\n   - **No wallet address set up** (X402_PAY_TO_ADDRESS is empty)\n   - **Payments not wired to ledger** (recordPayment() exists but isn't called)\n   - **No end-to-end testing** (even on testnet)\n   - **Not enabled in production** (Railway env vars not set)\n\n4. **The code is in `/Users/kublai/projects/parse-for-agents/`** - a separate project, not in the main Parse platform\n\n5. **The old prototype** in `_exiled` is archived/superseded\n\nNow I can give the human a clear status update as the project manager.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"**x402 Status: Code generated, not yet live.**\n\nHere's the current state:\n\n**Code: ~85% complete**\n- x402 middleware using official `@x402/hono` SDK ✓\n- Auth bypass for paid requests ✓\n- Payment ledger (in-memory) ✓\n- Pricing endpoints, dashboard integration ✓\n- Location: `/Users/kublai/projects/parse-for-agents/`\n\n**Blockers to going live:**\n1. **No Base L2 wallet** — Need to create/designate wallet for receiving USDC\n2. **Not enabled in production** — Railway missing `X402_ENABLED=true` and `X402_PAY_TO_ADDRESS=0x...`\n3. **Payment ledger not wired** — `recordPayment()` exists but isn't called from middleware\n4. **No end-to-end test** — Not tested even on Base Sepolia testnet\n\n**Next steps:**\n1. Set up Base L2 wallet (Coinbase Smart Wallet or EOA)\n2. Wire `recordPayment()` into middleware callback\n3. Test